{
  "texts": [
    "This task aims to provide a means for evaluating prediction models as new knowledge becomes available over time.",
    "Results from this task will provide insight into the usefulness of the PheKnowLator builds and will be used to identify areas where the ecosystem can be improved.",
    "Additionally, subsets of prebuilt PheKnowLator KGs have been used to help develop and evaluate novel, cutting-edge graph embedding AI tools (i.e., GRAPE 49), including random-walk-based embedding methods for extremely large-scale heterogeneous graphs using the PheKnowLator KG builds 50.",
    "In addition to graph representation learning, prebuilt PheKnowLator KGs were used for prototyping a novel method for knowledge-driven mechanistic enrichment of ignorome genes (i.e., differentially expressed genes which are associated with a disease experimentally but that have no known association to the disease in the literature) 51.",
    "When applied to preeclampsia, this method was able to identify 53 novel clinically relevant and biologically actionable disease associations."
  ]
}